entries.content: On the AFofM Recording Report of this date, DE6114a is listed as "Asphalt Jungle Theme Part I" (remake of June 1); DE6114b is listed as "Asphalt Jungle Theme Part II, Version I" and DE6114c is listed as "Asphalt Jungle Theme Part II, Version II", but they are issued as "Asphalt Jungle Theme Part I and Part II" on Co 4-42144. The doubt persists that 6114a instead of 6114b was published in Co 4-42144. DE6114c is titled "Asphalt Jungle Twist" on Co CL-1765 and CBS 62993.
